data.description: Remarkable Santa Fe haven situated on 2.5 acres, offering a front row seat to Enchanting NM scenery, turquoise skies and vivid sunsets. Traditional Northern NM/Santa Fe luxury and style around every sleek corner. Circle drive entry around flagstone patio and Spanish Fountain. Brick pavers at entry wrap around to back patio. The gourmet kitchen flows into living and dining room. Comfortable Family room and 2 bedrooms with private baths are also located on main level, there is a powder room on main level. Upstairs you will find the Primary suite, private sunroom with year-round hot tub, complete with personal sauna and access to Upper deck off the suite. Summer can't get here fast enough; covered patio, pool and outdoor kitchen are perfect for at home entertaining during the warmer months.
